                      "text": "December 26, 2021",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Where light can barely reach, a treacherous foe lies in wait in the shadows.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "In a realm void of sunlight, the remaining kindlings still burn.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "And where the sun shines, people's hopes spring eternal.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "These heartfelt wishes sparkle as bright as fireworks blooming in the sky.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
